headline.main: UConn Beats UCF in AAC Semifinal for 106th Straight Win
headline.print_headline: UConn Beats UCF in AAC Semifinal for 106th Straight Win

lead_paragraph: UConn brushed aside a physical challenge from UCF to move back into the final of the American Athletic Conference Tournament.
